"tag-wrongdoing-al-thulm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2Ca","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":6647,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/18\/allah-retaliates-for-beating\/","url_meta":{"origin":10054,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Beatings: Allah retaliates for those beaten","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever strikes\u00a0someone unjustly will receive retribution for it on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 186 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0636\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0636\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064b\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/most-beloved-best-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":10054,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The Prophet&#8217;s beloved have best character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I tell you about the most beloved to me and the closest to my assembly on the Day of Resurrection? Those with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 272 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/animals-complain-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":10054,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Animals: Oppressed animals testify on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sharid ibn Suwayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever kills so much as a sparrow unjustly, it will plead to Allah on the Day of Resurrection, saying: O Lord, he killed me unjustly, and he did not kill me for any beneficial purpose!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/two-faces-tongues-of-fire\/","url_meta":{"origin":10054,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Two-Faces: Hypocrites with two-faces given tongues of Fire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ammar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever carries two faces in the world, he will have two tongues of fire on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4873 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40829,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/28\/rahmah-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":10054,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Animals: Be merciful even as you slaughter for food","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 28, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is merciful, even as he slaughters his animal, then Allah will be merciful to him on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 381 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17053,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/29\/salat-nur-burhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":10054,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Gua